Apartment for Rent in Vedado
 Independent Apartment for Rent in Vedado, small ocean view, near the Malecón of Havana City and near the Meliá Cohiba Hotel. It includes two bedrooms with air-conditioning and matrimonial beds, kitchen with gas stove and kitchen utensils, living-diner, and a bathroom with cold and hot water round the clock. WIFI one block away.
If you want to rent only one bedroom the price is 30cuc per diem (daily) and the other bedroom it would be closed so you can keep your privacy, but if you want to rent the two of them the price would be 50cuc per diem. 
The apartment includes telephone, fan refrigerator, TV, rice pot and others facilities.
Address: #532, 8 Street, between 1st and 3rd, apartment #7, Vedado, Havana.
